scene.message:
Tadashi: Ah! {ctl0f:1}! What's{nl}
it like out there, huh? You{nl}
were outside, right?{waitkey}Was my bald old man alive?{waitkey}{ret}

Tamaki: Heh~ You're scared,{nl}
aren't you? Why don't you go{nl}
look for yourself?{waitkey}Coward Tadashi!{waitkey}{ret}

Tadashi: Y-you idiot! I-I'm{nl}
not scared of any demons!{nl}
You're way scarier!{waitkey}You muscle-bound girl!{waitkey}{ret}

Tamaki: What did you say!{nl}
You coward! Coward coward{nl}
coward coward coward coward!{waitkey}{ret}

Tadashi: Argh! You muscle{nl}
girl! Muscle girl muscle girl{nl}
muscle girl muscle giirl!{waitkey}Th-that's a mouthful...{waitkey}{ret}

Tadashi: Huff... wheeze...{wait_fr:88}{nl}
What an uncute girl,{nl}
honestly. You think so{nl}
too, {ctl0f:1}?{waitkey}{ret}

Tamaki: Huff, huff, huff...{wait_fr:88}{nl}
...Hey, {ctl0f:1}. I'll give{nl}
you this.{waitkey}{clearbox}It's something I used at my{nl}
old school, for reasons...{nl}
This time it's your turn,{nl}
not mine.{waitkey}I've got that feeling...{waitkey}{ret}

Tamaki: {ctl0f:1}, some demons{nl}
are the reasonable sort.{waitkey}Remember — defeating them{nl}
isn't the only path.{waitkey}{ret}

Male Member: Tamaki's{nl}
incredible. Just now she{nl}
named off the demons walking{nl}
outside one by one!{waitkey}{clearbox}Said this one's useful, that{nl}
one won't become an ally, and{nl}
so on. By the way, what's{nl}
an "ally"?{waitkey}{ret}

{color:3}Tamaki{nl}
A transfer student in the{nl}
fencing club. Quarrels with{nl}
Tadashi every day.{color:0}{waitkey}{ret}

{color:2}Tadashi{nl}
A lazy member of the fencing{nl}
club. Quarrels with Tamaki{nl}
every day.{color:0}{waitkey}{ret}

Female Member: With them{nl}
bickering it felt like the{nl}
usual mood, but... something{nl}
big's happening now, huh.{waitkey}{ret}
